{"tid":1621110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超：警方可以蒙面執法確保人身安全","createTime":"2019-10-04T12:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:34:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c4536ac9b9434162b87d72632f5fb750360ed526","tid":1621110,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】保安局局長李家超說，警方有權要求市民除下蒙面物品，可免除查核市民身份的爭議，而警方執法時可以蒙面是因為需要合適保護裝備。<br />\n<br />\n6月起反修例遊行示威集會，參與市民除了戴了不同種類的口罩，還有人戴太陽眼鏡、帽等，在禁蒙面法下，怎樣才算犯法。<br />\n<br />\n禁蒙面法賦予警方權力，要求懷疑違法者，除下蒙面的物品，李家超指警方現時都有權查證市民身份，但新條例可免除爭議。不過李家超指警方可以蒙面執法，確保人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n禁蒙面法涵蓋範圍，包括獲不反對通知書的合法遊行及集會，李家超解釋，因應現時的遊行示威，最終都變成暴力事件。<br />\n<br />\n而香港即將踏入流感高峰期，李家超指若有合理辯解，而戴上口罩，法庭可以按個別情況，判斷是否合理辯護。"},{"pid":"579c07a93c1a48647f2a976a48dee5f0a99775aa","tid":1621110,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/editorsChoice/player?newsId=365110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365110&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=f654db08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365110&h=4c283abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/editorsChoice/player?newsId=365110</a>"},{"pid":"b09b51aba3f58ca3a3e017828463392059cdc1b8","tid":1621110,"uid":36845,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:26:40.000Z","msg":"哦，市民就唔洗確保人身安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d523df18fdaa4455a3140a4d6a4a857b4dcad3","tid":1621110,"uid":207858,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d787d42eb8417c0d7e5bc629baf1bded4a76923","tid":1621110,"uid":1358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"r